item.title: ICUAFC go on tour to Brighton’s beachside clubs... And play some football as well.
item.author: Mohammad Butt,
item.description: After weeks of deliberation and minutes of research, tour secretary Naven Ghulam came to the decision that Imperial College Union Association Football Club (ICUAFC) and its hordes of Rangers were to return to the tour destination from two years ago: the lovely sea side town of Brighton. The day …
